```catala
#[test]
declaration scope A:
  output w content integer

scope A:
  definition w equals
    if 1 > 2 or 2 > 3 then
      3
    else 4
```

```catala-test-cli
$ catala Typecheck --check-invariants
┌─[RESULT]─
│ All invariant checks passed
└─
┌─[RESULT]─
│ Typechecking successful!
└─
```

```catala-test-cli
$ catala test-scope A
┌─[RESULT]─ A ─
│ w = 6
└─
```
